official_title: A bill to provide for access to all duly licensed providers of health services without prior referral in the Federal employee health benefits program.

summary.text: Permits access to Federal employees or their beneficiaries or family members to all duly licensed providers of health services without prior referral in the Federal employee health benefits program. (Amends 5 U.S.C. 8902)
